		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Gauntlet was also released on <a href="http://bootgod.dyndns.org:7777/profile.php?id=2890" class="postlink">TR1ROM</a>, using the MMC3.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


