	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It may be worth noting that using a NES to Famicom adapter may prevent four screen mode from working properly due to lazy adapter makers that don't connect the proper lines.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
